'''Amador Cisneros''' was a letterer who was employed with [[Dark Horse Comics]]. He was responsible for the lettering of [[Union 2|''Union'' 2]], ''[[Sergio Aragonés Stomps Star Wars]]'', ''[[The Bounty Hunters: Kenix Kil]]'' and ''[[Luke Skywalker's Walkabout]]''. The latter is reprinted in ''[[Star Wars: Luke Skywalker, Last Hope for the Galaxy]]''.

